I just published my first Atom plugin and I really wanted to get some feedback on it, so I thought I'd post it here!

https://atom.io/packages/atom-tracer

It's a "language agnostic framework for tracing variables inline". Currently only works for Python. I made it primarily for use as a teaching tool, but I'm curious to hear if you think it could have other uses (or if you think it would in fact hinder rather than help beginners to code, I'd love to hear your thoughts!)

posts.description: A language agnostic Atom package for tracing variables inline!
